<details style="background-color: #ececec; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 1px solid transparent; border-radius: 5px;">
<summary style="font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold;">‚ùì Do I need a class set of the Circuit Playground or the micro:bit?</summary>
 <div style="margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;">
    <p>

#### You **will** need a class set of the Circuit Playgrounds to teach Unit 6 - Option A OR a class set of the micro:bits to each Unit 6 - Option B of CS Discoveries. 

#### If you do not have access to either Circuit Playgrounds or micro:bits, you will be able to teach all units of CS Discoveries except Unit 6: Creating Apps with Devices. 
